{"translation-revision-date":"2026-06-17 11:04:09+0000","generator":"GlotPress\/4.0.3","domain":"messages","locale_data":{"messages":{"":{"domain":"messages","plural-forms":"nplurals=3; plural=(n == 1) ? 0 : ((n >= 2 && n <= 4) ? 1 : 2);","lang":"cs_CZ"},"A default term name is required.":["Je nutn\u00e9 zadat v\u00fdchoz\u00ed n\u00e1zev term\u00ednu."],"Once saved, updating the name creates a new term \u2014 the previous default term remains in the terms list. To change the term's slug or description, edit it from the terms list.":["Po ulo\u017een\u00ed se p\u0159i aktualizaci n\u00e1zvu vytvo\u0159\u00ed nov\u00fd term\u00edn \u2013 p\u016fvodn\u00ed v\u00fdchoz\u00ed term\u00edn z\u016fstane v seznamu term\u00edn\u016f. Chcete-li zm\u011bnit slug nebo popis term\u00ednu, upravte jej v seznamu term\u00edn\u016f."],"Default term name":["V\u00fdchoz\u00ed n\u00e1zev obdob\u00ed"],"Default term to be used for the taxonomy, similar to how \"Uncategorized\" works for categories.":["V\u00fdchoz\u00ed n\u00e1zev, kter\u00fd se m\u00e1 pro taxonomii pou\u017e\u00edt, podobn\u011b jako u kategori\u00ed funguje polo\u017eka \u201eNeza\u0159azen\u00e9\u201c."],"Set a default term":["Nastavit v\u00fdchoz\u00ed term\u00edn"],"Whether terms in this taxonomy should be saved in the order they are assigned to an item.":["Zda by se term\u00edny v t\u00e9to taxonomii m\u011bly ukl\u00e1dat v po\u0159ad\u00ed, v jak\u00e9m jsou p\u0159i\u0159azeny k polo\u017ece."],"Sort terms":["T\u0159\u00eddit podle"],"View Posts":["Zobrazit p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky"],"View posts":["Zobrazit p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky"],"Where this taxonomy appears: REST API, admin UI, and front-end surfaces.":["Kde se tato taxonomie vyskytuje: v rozhran\u00ed REST API, v administra\u010dn\u00edm rozhran\u00ed a ve front-endov\u00fdch rozhran\u00edch."],"Whether terms can be displayed in the Tag Cloud widget.":["Zda lze term\u00edny zobrazit v widgetu \u201eTag Cloud\u201c."],"Available in Tag Cloud widget":["K dispozici ve widgetu \u201eTag Cloud\u201c"],"Whether terms are selectable in the theme nav menu builder.":["Zda lze polo\u017eky vyb\u00edrat v n\u00e1stroji pro tvorbu naviga\u010dn\u00edho menu motivu."],"Available in nav menus":["Dostupn\u00e9 v naviga\u010dn\u00edch nab\u00eddk\u00e1ch"],"Whether to display a column for the taxonomy on the associated post type list tables.":["Zda se m\u00e1 ve v\u00fdpisov\u00fdch tabulk\u00e1ch p\u0159\u00edslu\u0161n\u00e9ho typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku zobrazit sloupec pro taxonomii."],"Show admin column":["Zobrazit sloupec spr\u00e1vce"],"Show in Quick Edit":["Zobrazit v rychl\u00e9 \u00faprav\u011b"],"Whether to show the taxonomy in the admin menu. Has no effect when Show admin UI is off; the value is preserved either way.":["Zda se m\u00e1 taxonomie zobrazovat v administr\u00e1torsk\u00e9m menu. Nem\u00e1 \u017e\u00e1dn\u00fd vliv, pokud je mo\u017enost Zobrazit administr\u00e1torsk\u00e9 rozhran\u00ed vypnut\u00e1; hodnota z\u016fstane zachov\u00e1na v ka\u017ed\u00e9m p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b."],"Show in admin menu":["Zobrazit v nab\u00eddce pro spr\u00e1vce"],"Whether to generate a default admin interface for managing terms.":["Zda se m\u00e1 vygenerovat v\u00fdchoz\u00ed administr\u00e1torsk\u00e9 rozhran\u00ed pro spr\u00e1vu term\u00edn\u016f."],"Show admin UI":["Zobrazit rozhran\u00ed pro spr\u00e1vu"],"Whether front-end queries (e.g. ?taxonomy=\u2026&term=\u2026) can return terms from this taxonomy.":["Zda dotazy na stran\u011b front-endu (nap\u0159. ?taxonomy=\u2026&term=\u2026) mohou vracet term\u00edny z t\u00e9to taxonomie."],"Publicly queryable":["Dostupn\u00e9 k ve\u0159ejn\u00e9mu vyhled\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed"],"Required for the block editor. Turn off only for taxonomies that should not be exposed via REST.":["Nezbytn\u00e9 pro blokov\u00fd editor. Vypn\u011bte pouze u taxonomi\u00ed, kter\u00e9 nemaj\u00ed b\u00fdt zp\u0159\u00edstupn\u011bny p\u0159es REST."],"View terms":["Zobrazit podm\u00ednky"],"Duplicate taxonomy":["Duplicitn\u00ed taxonomie"],"Failed to duplicate taxonomy.":["Duplikov\u00e1n\u00ed taxonomie se nezda\u0159ilo."],"taxonomy\u0004%s (Copy)":["%s (Kop\u00edrovat)"],"Failed to create post type.":["Vytvo\u0159en\u00ed typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku se nezda\u0159ilo."],"Core identity, taxonomies, supports, and activation.":["Z\u00e1kladn\u00ed identita, taxonomie, podp\u016frn\u00e9 prvky a aktivace."],"Edit this post type. Expand the Labels section to adjust labels.":["Upravte tento typ p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku. Rozbalte sekci \u0160t\u00edtky a upravte \u0161t\u00edtky."],"Define a new post type. Fill in the essentials under General; expand Labels to customize.":["Definujte nov\u00fd typ p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku. Vypl\u0148te z\u00e1kladn\u00ed \u00fadaje v sekci Obecn\u00e9; rozbalte sekci \u0160t\u00edtky a prove\u010fte p\u0159izp\u016fsoben\u00ed."],"Quick edit post type":["Rychl\u00e1 \u00faprava typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku"],"Failed to update post type.":["Aktualizaci typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku se nepoda\u0159ilo prov\u00e9st."],"\"%s\" post type updated.":["Typ p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku \u201e%s\u201c byl aktualizov\u00e1n."],"Override the text WordPress shows in admin lists, menus, and forms. Auto-fill replaces every label below with values derived from the current plural and singular names \u2014 including any you have already customized. Clearing removes all overrides so WordPress falls back to its defaults. If you rename the post type after auto-filling, click Auto-fill again to keep them in sync.":["P\u0159epi\u0161te text, kter\u00fd WordPress zobrazuje v administr\u00e1torsk\u00fdch seznamech, nab\u00eddk\u00e1ch a formul\u00e1\u0159\u00edch. Funkce Automatick\u00e9 vypln\u011bn\u00ed nahrad\u00ed v\u0161echny n\u00ed\u017ee uveden\u00e9 popisky hodnotami odvozen\u00fdmi od aktu\u00e1ln\u00edch n\u00e1zv\u016f v jednotn\u00e9m a mno\u017en\u00e9m \u010d\u00edsle \u2013 v\u010detn\u011b t\u011bch, kter\u00e9 jste ji\u017e p\u0159izp\u016fsobili. Tla\u010d\u00edtko Vymazat odstran\u00ed v\u0161echna p\u0159eps\u00e1n\u00ed, tak\u017ee se WordPress vr\u00e1t\u00ed k v\u00fdchoz\u00edm nastaven\u00edm. Pokud po automatick\u00e9m vypln\u011bn\u00ed p\u0159ejmenujete typ p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku, klikn\u011bte znovu na tla\u010d\u00edtko Automatick\u00e9 vypln\u011bn\u00ed, aby se \u00fadaje synchronizovaly."],"Screen reader text for the admin list table.":["Text pro \u010dte\u010dku obrazovky u tabulky se seznamem spr\u00e1vc\u016f."],"Items list":["Seznam polo\u017eek"],"Screen reader text for the admin list pagination.":["Text pro \u010dte\u010dku obrazovky t\u00fdkaj\u00edc\u00ed se str\u00e1nkov\u00e1n\u00ed seznamu spr\u00e1vc\u016f."],"Items list navigation":["Navigace v seznamu polo\u017eek"],"Screen reader text for the admin list filter controls.":["Text pro \u010dte\u010dku obrazovky u ovl\u00e1dac\u00edch prvk\u016f filtru v seznamu spr\u00e1vce."],"Filter posts list":["Filtrovat seznam p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f"],"Filter items list":["Seznam polo\u017eek filtru"],"Uploaded to this post":["P\u0159id\u00e1no k tomuto p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku"],"Uploaded to this item":["Nahr\u00e1no k tomuto polo\u017ece"],"Shown in the media library uploader.":["Zobrazeno v n\u00e1stroji pro nahr\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed do medi\u00e1ln\u00ed knihovny."],"Insert into post":["Vlo\u017eit do p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku"],"Insert into item":["Vlo\u017eit do polo\u017eky"],"Shown above the parent dropdown. Not used on non-hierarchical post types.":["Zobrazuje se nad rozbalovac\u00edm seznamem nad\u0159azen\u00fdch polo\u017eek. U nehierarchick\u00fdch typ\u016f p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f se nepou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1."],"Parent Page:":["Nad\u0159azen\u00e1 str\u00e1nka:"],"Title of the Attributes meta box. Not used on non-hierarchical post types.":["N\u00e1zev meta pole \u201eAtributy\u201c. Nepou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 se u nehierarchick\u00fdch typ\u016f p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f."],"Post Attributes":["Atributy p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku"],"Used in the navigation menus block when adding a link to the post type archive.":["Pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 se v bloku naviga\u010dn\u00edch nab\u00eddek p\u0159i p\u0159id\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed odkazu do archivu typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku."],"Post Archives":["Archiv p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f"],"No posts found in Trash.":["V ko\u0161i nebyly nalezeny \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e9 p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky."],"Not found in trash":["Nenalezeno v ko\u0161i"],"Shown in the admin list when no posts match.":["Zobraz\u00ed se v seznamu spr\u00e1vce, pokud nejsou nalezeny \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e9 p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky."],"Search Posts":["Vyhledat p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky"],"Used as the link label for the post type archive.":["Pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 se jako n\u00e1zev odkazu pro archiv typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku."],"View items":["Zobrazit polo\u017eky"],"New item":["Nov\u00fd produkt"],"Edit Post":["Upravit p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvek"],"Shown in the admin menu and on toolbar buttons.":["Zobrazuje se v nab\u00eddce pro spr\u00e1vu a na tla\u010d\u00edtk\u00e1ch na panelu n\u00e1stroj\u016f."],"View pages":["Zobrazit str\u00e1nky"],"Duplicate post type":["Duplicitn\u00ed typ p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku"],"Failed to duplicate post type.":["Duplikov\u00e1n\u00ed typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku se nezda\u0159ilo."],"\"%s\" post type created.":["Byl vytvo\u0159en typ p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku \u201e%s\u201c."],"post type\u0004%s (Copy)":["%s (Kop\u00edrovat)"],"One or more taxonomies that should be associated with this post type.":["Jedna nebo v\u00edce taxonomi\u00ed, kter\u00e9 by m\u011bly b\u00fdt p\u0159i\u0159azeny k tomuto typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku."],"This post type key is already in use.":["Tento kl\u00ed\u010d typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku je ji\u017e pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1n."],"Lower case letters, numbers, underscores, and dashes only. Maximum length: 20 characters.":["Pouze mal\u00e1 p\u00edsmena, \u010d\u00edslice, podtr\u017e\u00edtka a poml\u010dky. Maxim\u00e1ln\u00ed d\u00e9lka: 20 znak\u016f."],"Changing the key renames the post type \u2014 existing posts may become inaccessible until a migration updates the database.":["Zm\u011bna kl\u00ed\u010de zp\u016fsob\u00ed p\u0159ejmenov\u00e1n\u00ed typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku \u2013 st\u00e1vaj\u00edc\u00ed p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky mohou b\u00fdt nedostupn\u00e9, dokud migrace neaktualizuje datab\u00e1zi."],"Post type key":["Kl\u00ed\u010d typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku"],"Editor features and metadata enabled for posts of this type.":["Pro p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky tohoto typu jsou povoleny funkce editoru a metadata."],"Supports":["Podporuje"],"Required for the block editor. Disable only if posts of this type should not be available via the REST API.":["Nezbytn\u00e9 pro blokov\u00fd editor. Deaktivujte pouze v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b, \u017ee p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky tohoto typu nemaj\u00ed b\u00fdt dostupn\u00e9 prost\u0159ednictv\u00edm REST API."],"Show in REST API":["Zobrazit v REST API"],"Whether the post type has an archive page (e.g. \/book\/). Requires permalink rewrite rules to be flushed after enabling.":["Zda m\u00e1 dan\u00fd typ p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku archivn\u00ed str\u00e1nku (nap\u0159. \/book\/). Po aktivaci je nutn\u00e9 vypr\u00e1zdnit pravidla pro p\u0159episov\u00e1n\u00ed trval\u00fdch odkaz\u016f."],"Has archive":["Obsahuje archiv"],"When on, posts of this type can have parent-child relationships like pages, and the parent picker is shown in the editor. When off, they behave like posts.":["Je-li tato funkce zapnut\u00e1, mohou p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky tohoto typu m\u00edt nad\u0159azen\u00e9 a pod\u0159azen\u00e9 vztahy stejn\u011b jako str\u00e1nky a v editoru se zobraz\u00ed v\u00fdb\u011br nad\u0159azen\u00e9 polo\u017eky. Je-li vypnut\u00e1, chovaj\u00ed se jako b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky."],"Whether the post type is intended for use publicly either via the admin interface or by front-end users.":["Zda je typ p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku ur\u010den k ve\u0159ejn\u00e9mu pou\u017eit\u00ed, a to bu\u010f prost\u0159ednictv\u00edm administr\u00e1torsk\u00e9ho rozhran\u00ed, nebo u\u017eivateli na stran\u011b front-endu."],"Optional summary of the post type. Shown in admin UIs that surface post type details.":["Voliteln\u00fd popis typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku. Zobrazuje se v administra\u010dn\u00edm rozhran\u00ed, kter\u00e9 zobrazuje podrobnosti o typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku."],"Post formats":["Form\u00e1ty p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f"],"Trackbacks":["Odkazy"],"%s list":["Seznam %s"],"%s list navigation":["%s \u2013 navigace v seznamu"],"Filter %s list":["Filtrovat seznam %s"],"Use as featured image":["Pou\u017e\u00edt jako \u00favodn\u00ed obr\u00e1zek"],"Uploaded to this %s":["Nahr\u00e1no do tohoto %s"],"Insert into %s":["Vlo\u017ete do %s"],"%s Attributes":["Atributy %s"],"%s Archives":["Archiv %s"],"No %s found in Trash.":["V ko\u0161i nebyl nalezen \u017e\u00e1dn\u00fd soubor %s."],"+%d":["procent"],"Enabled and registered with WordPress when active.":["Je-li tato funkce aktivn\u00ed, je v syst\u00e9mu WordPress povolena a zaregistrov\u00e1na."],"Some errors occurred while deleting the post types: %s":["P\u0159i maz\u00e1n\u00ed typ\u016f p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f do\u0161lo k n\u011bkolika chyb\u00e1m: %s"],"Failed to delete post types.":["Nepoda\u0159ilo se odstranit typy p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f."],"Failed to delete post type.":["Nepoda\u0159ilo se odstranit typ p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku."],"\"%s\" post type deleted.":["Typ p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku \u201e%s\u201c byl smaz\u00e1n."],"Some errors occurred while deactivating the post types: %s":["P\u0159i deaktivaci typ\u016f p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f do\u0161lo k n\u011bkolika chyb\u00e1m: %s"],"An error occurred while deactivating the post type: %s":["P\u0159i deaktivaci typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku do\u0161lo k chyb\u011b: %s"],"Failed to deactivate post types.":["Nepoda\u0159ilo se deaktivovat typy p\u0159\